snippet.title: In Flight Pac-Man
snippet.description: Hi! It's me playing Pac-Man on the plane :p lol I'm so lucky that I find pac-man game wherever I go! I can do better than this game play, but when I recorded this video I wasn't focused because I was tired and I was holding my mobile to record.
